==Reception==
The game has received generally negative reviews, most of them varying around 3 and 5, resulting on a [[Metacritic]] score of 36/100.

[[Scott Jones]] and [[Victor Lucas]] from [[Reviews on the Run]], though, both gave the game a 0.0/10 rating saying the best word to describe the game is "pathetic", while [[GamesRadar]] web site game it a 7/10 saying on its veredict that it is "Overall fun and deceptively deep".

